flowchart LR
    subgraph "Browser"
        S1["sessionStorage<br/>svu_csrf_token = fp:token"]
        S2["Cookie<br/>svu_csrf_token = fp:token<br/>SameSite=Lax; Secure on HTTPS"]
        FP["Browser fingerprint<br/>(UA,lang,tz,screen)"]
    end

    subgraph "csrf.js"
        GT["getCsrfToken()"]
        SC["setCsrfCookie()"]
        AP["applyCsrfToSupabase()"]
    end

    subgraph "Supabase Client"
        Q1["db.from(table).select()"]
        Q2["db.from(table).insert()"]
        Q3["Any DB query"]
    end

    FP -->|"hash"| GT
    GT -->|"store proxy token"| S1
    GT -->|"set cookie"| SC
    SC -->|"write cookie"| S2
    GT -->|"intercept query builder"| AP
    AP -->|"add x-csrf-token"| Q1
    AP -->|"add x-csrf-token"| Q2
    AP -->|"add x-csrf-token"| Q3

    note right of AP
        Monkey-patches db.from() builder
        to attach CSRF header to every
        query without manual setup.
    end note

    note right of Q3
        send request
        ├── Cookie: svu_csrf_token=fp:token
        └── Header: x-csrf-token=<token>
    end note
